main event: UFO sighting recorded by radar on October 31, 1960, passing 30-35 NM south of the observers' location.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 1 minute and involved 2 unusual radar targets., The radar tracked the unidentified airborne object moving at a speed of 3962 KTS., The object was at an unknown altitude., Possible atmospheric conditions were suggested as a cause for the observation., The sighting is part of historical records from Project Blue Book.
sighted object: Unidentified airborne object detected by radar
